title: (APPS) Southern-Lights--1.0.7.zip
description:
For all you folks that are begging ppl for Northern Lights and not getting it! Here is somthing better! its called Southern Lights! Southern Lights is a program that displays the Winamp song when you change it! No button pressing or anything and no bot setting! Here are the main Features

Features
+ Able to Pick to send to all channels your are in or the selected one you selected from the list
+ Support for WCS, MCS, Ouka, And Just regular Winmx
+ Automatically Sends the new song playing to the channel
